item.title: Love Vibes
item.description: [Intro] Eo, I said eo I get lalala love vibes Lalalala from you Eo, I said eo I get lalala love vibes Lalalala from you [Verse 1] I felt that I'm all alone In a place so cold, no love I had nowhere else to go She came to me like a dream Like an angel I haven’t seen She sang to me sweet melody [Pre-Chorus] I don't wanna let you go now I think you're my destiny Trying to show me something I don’t really wanna see I don't wanna let you go now Will you remember me?
